homes.title: Grand Villa
homes.description: The house has two floors with 4 bedrooms, large social areas and a large kitchen. The area around the house is quiet and comfortable with both meadow and forest environment. Nearby in the farm forestry is an old mill pond with a small overnight cabin, barbecue area, and jetty where you can swim. There are berries and mushrooms for picking in the woods in season. Fishing with a fishing license is possible in nearby lakes.
